(I better write a receipt for a loan.)

15
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,560
(Like a loan.)

16
00:01:25,720 --> 00:01:28,000
(I think I've seen this paper before.)

17
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,920
(It's the letter Dullard gave me.)

18
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,400
(What a coincidence.)

19
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,920
(Maybe the papers in the palace
all look the same.)

20
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:49,020
[Receipt for a loan]

21
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,960
(Chief Eunuch instructed
to watch over her.)

22
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:52,200
(Why did you come out?)

23
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,160
She fainted.

24
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,560
It's going to be long sleep.

25
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,560
(Forget it.)

26
00:01:58,560 --> 00:02:01,160
(It's better to run now.)

27
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:10,560
[Ancestral Hall]
Murong, you went to great lengths

28
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:13,040
to flush the mole out.

29
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:15,760
Why did you kill him?

30
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:18,360
[Memorial Tablet of Mother, Yun'niang]
(He crossed the line.)

31
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,800
(The situation was critical back then.)

32
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:21,640
(The murderer who harmed the Mu clan)

33
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:23,400
(had been on the prowl for me.)

34
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:26,120
(With the help of my father's friend,
Imperial Physician Yang,)

35
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,360
(I escaped castration)

36
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:29,400
(and hid in the palace as a eunuch.)

37
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,440
(I've been investigating the murder,)

38
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:32,880
(hoping to bring the culprit to justice)

39
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:34,680
(one day.)

40
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,200
I brought you this medication.

41
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:38,440
[Spy]
Have your men prepare this.

42
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:47,320
Thank you, Uncle Yang.

43
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:50,640
Your father, Imperial Physician Mu,
saved my life.

44
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,880
I see him as my family.

45
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:53,960
Before we get our revenge,

46
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:55,920
I won't let anyone kill you.

47
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,840
I will protect you

48
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,200
even at the cost of my life.

49
00:02:59,320 --> 00:02:59,960
Uncle Yang.

50
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:02,640
I was desperate back then.

51
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:04,160
It was you who sent me to the palace

52
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,680
and helped me avoid castration.

53
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,400
It's all thanks to you

54
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,320
that I have reached this far.

55
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:12,760
Don't underestimate the culprit
behind this poisoning incident.

56
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:13,880
I know very well

57
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,080
who did this.

58
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:17,400
I need a reason to take them down.

59
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:21,600
Mu and Yun'niang.

60
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:23,520
Departed souls of the Mu clan,

61
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,320
[Memorial Tablet of Father Mu Yinyuan]
please bless Mu

62
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:26,840
[Memorial Tablet of Father Mu Yinyuan]
to purge the evil,

63
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,480
clear the name of the Mu clan,

64
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:32,040
and restore peace to the Yin Dynasty.

65
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,280
(It seems)

66
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:44,360
(that I could get out of here today.)

67
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,280
Jixiang.

68
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:48,640
Jixiang.

69
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,840
(Oh, no. Busted.)

70
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:53,600
(This is the only way to save myself.)

71
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:22,720
Jixiang.

72
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:34,720
That's a rare expression on your face.

73
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,360
Jixiang.

74
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,200
This is Imperial Physician Yang.

75
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:43,400
He's not a bad person.

76
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:46,040
Besides, he's skilled.

77
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,760
I believe he could restore your sanity.

78
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,360
This girl

79
00:05:00,280 --> 00:05:01,240
is hopeless.

80
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,680
I can't do anything about it.

81
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,040
Thank you so much,
Imperial Physician Yang.

82
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,480
I'll take my leave.

83
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,840
Please take care, Mr. Yang.

84
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:45,320
Since the physician said
you're hopeless,

85
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,400
keeping you here is no use.

86
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:47,520
You may leave.

87
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,200
Really?

88
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,320
I'm leaving, then.

89
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,480
Stop right there.

90
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,720
You understood

91
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,760
my words, though.

92
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:02,320
(He got me good.)

93
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:13,080
Godfather.

94
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:15,920
Ask me anything you want to know.

95
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:18,720
I'll tell you everything
as much as I know.

96
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,840
If it wasn't for you yesterday,

97
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:22,520
Ankang would've killed me.

98
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,920
How did you find that out?

99
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:30,640
Speaking of this,

100
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:32,040
I bet you know

101
00:06:32,520 --> 00:06:36,080
I'm the well-known soothsayer
in Longevity Shrine.

102
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,040
I didn't know that,

103
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:39,560
nor had I heard it before.

104
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:41,680
Anyway,

105
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:43,880
when I touch someone

106
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,320
with my hand,

107
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,480
I could foresee their future.

108
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:57,560
Now tell me.

109
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,160
What did you see?

110
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:01,280
(Murong Cang is eccentric.)

111
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:03,600
(If I were to tell me
that his future is a mess,)

112
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,880
(he would probably think I lied.)

113
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:05,920
(I might lose my life.)

114
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:08,400
(I'd rather take my chances.)

115
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:10,400
I saw

116
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:13,760
that you'll fall deeply for me.

117
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:14,600
You love me

118
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,240
in spite of yourself.

119
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:17,600
Nonsense!

120
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,240
There's something else.

121
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:21,800
You wouldn't want to beat me

122
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,160
or scold me.

123
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,440
Lowly maid.

124
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:29,120
How dare you slander Chief Eunuch!

125
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,880
This is demeaning.

126
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:31,720
You deserve a thousand deaths.

127
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:35,640
Chief Eunuch, she...

128
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,120
You said

129
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,360
that I would fall for you,

130
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:44,600
then why did you insist
on returning to the shrine?

131
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:48,040
I...

132
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,400
By any chance,

133
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:52,880
does your lover stay there?

134
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,640
That's not true.

135
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:57,360
I'm waiting for someone.

136
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,080
Waiting for someone?

137
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:00,960
Hmm.

138
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,880
If that person

139
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:04,960
really cares for you
more than anything else,

140
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,520
you wouldn't have to wait.

141
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,280
Since you said
that I would fall for you.

142
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,000
Tonight,

143
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:13,000
you're going to serve in my room.

144
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,000
- What?
- What?

145
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:18,320
Don't make me wait.

146
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:21,560
Otherwise, I'll kill you

147
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:23,200
before I fall in love with you.

148
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:25,000
All right.

149
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,840
This is strange.

150
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:35,120
Chief Eunuch never allows anyone
to serve in his room.

151
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,240
Why did he let her in?

152
00:08:37,560 --> 00:08:40,320
Did this girl bewitch him?

153
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:41,600
The two of them...

154
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:45,920
What has gotten into me?

155
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,400
Chief Eunuch is a eunuch like me.

156
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:51,400
Women can't bewitch him.

157
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,240
Never.

158
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:58,840
Since

159
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:01,080
you predicted
that I would fall in love with you,

160
00:09:01,280 --> 00:09:03,080
you shouldn't go back
to Longevity Shrine.

161
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:06,040
I don't like disloyal servants.

162
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:08,800
(You actually believed in that?)

163
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:10,760
(Fake eunuch, it's not going to happen.)

164
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:14,640
Godfather, it's late now.

165
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:15,720
Please have a rest.

166
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,880
I should get going.

167
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:19,520
Continue.

168
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:22,680
Yes.

169
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:23,800
Previously,

170
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:26,600
you sang a nursery rhyme
in Longevity Shrine.

171
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,280
Sing that again.

172
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:36,920
Godfather, you're the most powerful man
below the emperor,

173
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:39,320
and an intrepid warrior.

174
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:41,400
You like nursery rhymes?

175
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,240
If you don't want to sing,

176
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,400
I'll snip your tongue

177
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:48,040
to keep you silent.

178
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:49,640
No.

179
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,800
I want to sing.

180
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,280
I'm going to sing now.

181
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:59,040
♪Winter breathes plum blossom scent♪

182
