♪That illuminate the night♪

186
00:10:16,300 --> 00:10:21,060
♪Ushering you into the slumberland♪

187
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:27,960
Dullard, will you stay with me forever?

188
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:30,880
No one can always stay with you.

189
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:33,840
I want to go home.

190
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,200
You don't have a home.

191
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,880
This is your home.

192
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,040
From now on,

193
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:48,040
