194
00:10:52,880 --> 00:10:54,480
What did you say?

195
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,840
Nothing.

196
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:03,680
I said I'm tired.

197
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,440
Please take a rest.

198
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,960
I'm leaving.

199
00:11:11,520 --> 00:11:12,400
Hold on.

200
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,480
What's the matter, Godfather?

201
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:21,760
I've thought

202
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,800
your prophecy through,

203
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,800
