204
00:11:26,980 --> 00:11:32,540
♪Strive to bloom in the empty city♪

205
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:34,560
From now on,

206
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:37,120
Chief Eunuch is your home.

207
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:41,600
Starting tonight,

208
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:44,320
